results.deck: A publisher re-releasing budget titles of older PC games
results.description: Sold Out Sales & Marketing Ltd. is a publishing division of the Mastertronic group, re-releasing games for the PC at budget prices. Their first budget re-release was Jimmy White's Whirlwind Snooker in 1991.
